Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每当碰上这种报导
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就会拉上其他成员去对方办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要你废话 蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们也一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里是山区吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.86,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到是到了 但要等到后天才能外出
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今明两天都得上课
