Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}# 南极条约特征 *南极洲仅用于和平目的 *自由进行科学调查和促进国际间合作 *冻结领土主权的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那里和日本不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有许多制度和规则
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}趁这次集训好好记在心里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟学校里的你判若两人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们又不同班
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么首先和队长打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是南极观测队队长藤堂吟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}队长…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是女性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}丑话说在前头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管队员是随行人员还是研究人员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我都一视同仁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要做的事堆积如山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算你们是高中生 只要有需要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无论扫地 洗衣服 苦力活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们一个都别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把我的话记清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南极观测队员有个ABC准则
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A.这是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}B.别做傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}C.打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请把这三点谨记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:44.09,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪粗黑\bord0\1c&H3D423E&\frz20.47\frx358\fry356\pos(336,92)}１．想活下去\N\N２．想知道更多\N\N３．想扶持队友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:44.09,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪粗黑\bord0\1c&H3D423E&\frx4\fry0\frz18.24\pos(-4,400)}全部符合南极观测队。无论如何都要活下去、生还下来。\N保持对知识和经验的渴求。另外，不要孤立你的队友。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她好有队长风范啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像那种看到学生打瞌睡 就会扔粉笔的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是有考试 都是出超难的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对了 明天是训练开路工程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 要去外面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都来山里了 不出去走走就可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过这工程看来挺辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}久违的再会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说了 对所有队员一视同仁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.35,0:11:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是故意的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没 我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那孩子是靠自己来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过说实话 我早有预感了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从她第一次跟我说想一起去的时候起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她可是贵子的女儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像是收发器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个是指南针
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:12:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后这个是GPS定位装置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有旗子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向弄懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昨天基本上都教过了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是为什么要做这些事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南极是块平整的大陆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用开路也能走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为是平整又纯白的大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一旦下暴风雪就会迷失方向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以才要开路 方便沿着路走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怪不得要插这个旗子当路标
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是要插在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是要我们自己想 才有这个训练啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:34.22,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H3C3F40&\frx350\fry6\pos(768,156)\frz19.15}开路工程起点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:34.22,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H3C3F40&\frx350\fry6\pos(466,116)\frz20.46}通讯基地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:34.22,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs25\1c&H3C3F40&\frx350\fry6\frz23.13\pos(244,446)}下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里是我们目前的所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:39.83,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H3C3F40&\frz19.15\pos(586,246)\frx348\fry356}开路工程路线
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:39.83,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H3C3F40&\frx348\fry356\frz25.21\pos(80,244)}开路工程终点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:39.83,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3C3F40&\frx348\fry356\frz25.21\pos(350,652)}野营训练地点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后这边是目标地点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到那里去就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不单单是过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}途中的这里 这里和这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些地点都要插上旗子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别那么随随便便就行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道那些地点在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那边…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:12:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}…哎嘿？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}卖萌也没有用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用这个一边测量正确的地点一边前进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觉会很难耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}48 49 50
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看一下角度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用右眼看还是左眼看？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是惯用眼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}惯用眼是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我记得是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还没好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}168°
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再向右一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}右？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}右
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个右边？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}纬度是这个 经度是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是不是比刚才的距离更远啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果测量正确的话 应该在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那边吗…偏了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想起来自己当初刚参加时的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其他三个人是怎么进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不清楚 其中一个原本就要参加的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知什么时候她们变成朋友了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其他队员说要争取时间越短越好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我觉得准确度比速度更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毕竟安全第一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1 2…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}398 399 400
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}向左两步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过你居然知道小理很会用指南针啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是个直觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请叫我指南针的专家—「指南针女孩」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剪刀石头布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了 我是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像毕业旅行一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不打个牌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又不是来玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在帐篷里睡觉也是重要的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是现在还不到8点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想 队长也说合宿的晚上要开联欢会的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 快给我睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来聊聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讲鬼故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有点想杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道结月害怕鬼故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死请静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:10.57,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※结月本想说うるさい（吵死了），但这个词对学姐讲很没礼貌，临时改口说\N\h\h\h\h静かにしてください（请保持安静），结果把两个不相干的词组在了一起。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死请静是怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看你是学姐我才临时改口的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道我想表达什么意思就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死请静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别说啦 小理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑 睡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直想问个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑 你认识队长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么会这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:16:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个人是妈妈高中时的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和妈妈一起去了南极
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个人回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有妈妈没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为 妈妈还等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}满天繁星 北极星是哪一颗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像是在北斗七星某段的延长线上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.21,0:17:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟仙后座有关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那南极星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南极星？有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有倒是有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是不明显 比较难找到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从这里是看不到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要以为自己头顶上的群星就是全部的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是日向的名言吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}编得不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里是昭和基地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}极光队能听到吗 请回复
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里是极光队 我是三宅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}信号良好 请回复
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是定时联络
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有没有异常 请回复
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本日 极光队4名成员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人员设备均无异常 请回复
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}破晓时温度较低 注意保暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}定时联络结束 祝一切安好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}祝一切安好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好险 差点忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:57.70,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H403533&\pos(442,280)\frz18.96}新讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:57.70,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs40\1c&H726257&\frz18.96\pos(392,354)\frx348\fry350}收件人：{\1c&H403533&}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:57.70,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs40\1c&H726257&\frz18.96\frx348\fry350\pos(548,506)}主旨：{\1c&H403533&}致妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请问
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:20:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑的妈妈是怎样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.56,0:20:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我只能回答你 她是个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像报濑那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道 我不清楚她女儿是什么样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过她们的执着与死心眼 倒是像极了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真够麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:26.53,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}深夜零时の地平线　広がる世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:30.99,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}今日がずっと眩しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:41.76,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}鼻の奥がツンとした　きれいできれいで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:46.41,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}胸が痛くなるほどに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:56.00,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}両手いっぱいありったけの人に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:21:06.62,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}意味なんかないって言われ続けたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:19.18,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}宇宙(そら)から届くひかり　逆さまの星空见上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:23.21,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}ここから始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:31.75,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}さあ　迷いなんて置き去りにして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:38.38,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}探しに行くんだ　见果てぬ世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:47.02,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}さあ前を向いて　间违いなかったんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:53.38,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}言ってやるんだ　この思いが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:22:01.83,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}勇気出して　进んでいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:26.53,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}眼前是深夜零点的地平线 一片广大的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:30.99,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}今天一直是那么耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:41.76,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我激动得鼻尖一痒 眼前的景象是那么美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:46.41,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}灿烂到叫我心口作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:56.00,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}许许多多的人 装满双手也挤不下的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:21:06.62,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}都在劝我不要白费力气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:19.18,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}只是仰头看见那颠倒的星空 洒下的星光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:23.21,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我会从这里扬帆起航
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:31.75,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}把心里的迷茫留在岸边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:38.38,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}去探索广阔无垠 斑斓神秘的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:47.02,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}睁大眼睛直视前方 大声喊出
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:53.38,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}「我的执着没有错误！」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:22:01.83,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}拿出勇气 走出大大的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但麻烦点才好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的性格很适合去南极
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么要去南极
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被她叫来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是下决心的是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想和她一起去 不想就这样虚度高中生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想去见识不同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.92,0:20:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过认识了日向和结月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了观测队队员的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听了队长和报濑的事情后 我才觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:20:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是哪里都好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:20:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而是非南极不可！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想和大家一起去南极
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.53,0:21:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早起很难受的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了快起来 还有报濑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快点来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想和大家一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想和大家一起找到南极星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看极光 吃刨冰 和企鹅拍纪念照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们一定要去！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.32,0:21:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Comment: 0,0:22:05.04,0:22:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:25.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}长いトンネルの出口を探していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.27,0:22:36.81,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}かすかな光の匂いがしてる方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:42.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}间违っても　笑えるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:53.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}ここから始めよう　仆は旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.59,0:23:04.13,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}污れた真ん丸のビー玉　握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.29,0:23:15.40,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}言えなかった言叶も　きっと见つかるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.56,0:23:21.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}バカにされたって构わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.02,0:23:26.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}信じてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:25.89,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}寻找着漫长隧道的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.27,0:22:36.81,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}向着泛着微光气味的方向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:42.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}就算走错了 也别忘了微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:53.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}从这里开始 我将踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.59,0:23:04.13,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}紧紧捏住手心里 脏脏的玻璃珠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.29,0:23:15.40,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}没说出口的话 我也一定会找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.56,0:23:21.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}随你们嘲笑吧 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.02,0:23:26.35,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}要相信自己 迈出脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:38.07,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H8AA4A0&\pos(234,68)\frz13.84}好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:38.07,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H838D8B&\frz13.84\pos(662,660)}这里很美吧？
